snippet.title: B.I.O.T.A. Swarm - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: Check out the reveal trailer to see gameplay, alien enemies, and more from B.I.O.T.A. Swarm, an upcoming game that brings an arcade twist to Vampire Survivors-like titles. B.I.O.T.A. Swarm is coming to Steam in Q1 2023.
